  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>ERRE Spa facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>The hotel has a 2000 square metre spa. The Erre Spa has an indoor pool, sauna, whirlpools, emotional shower, Scottish shower (cold shower), Turkish bath and relaxation areas (open 10am - 8pm, bathrobes, towels and slippers are provided by the hotel, you must be over 16 years old to use the spa)</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Hotel facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Outdoor Swimming pool (normally open from May to September)</li>
<li>Pool bar (open from around June to September)</li>
<li>Scooter rental (payable locally)</li>
<li>20% discount on green fees at the nearby golf course, approx. three kilometres from the hotel</li>
<li>Garden</li>
<li>Gym</li>
<li>Free Wi-Fi</li>
<li>Parking (approx. €20 per night, subject to availability)</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
