  <listingDescription><![CDATA[<p>Grand Hotel Bristol Spa Resort stands out on Rapallo's coastline. It's a stunning Art Nouveau building with incredible outside areas and views of the Ligurian Riviera from all around. We love the pool that looks out over the Portofino Promontory. The rooftop a la carte restaurant is a must-try and you can't miss aperitivo in the bar at sunset.</p>]]></listingDescription>
