  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Prestige Rooms with Park Views </strong>sleep up to two people and have park views.</p>
<p><strong>Prestige Rooms with Partial Sea Views </strong>sleep up to two people and have partial sea views.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms with Sea Views </strong>sleep up to three people and are decorated in a classic style with light, sandy tones. The rooms look across to Rapallo and have sea views from the small French balcony. These rooms are also available for triple use, please call to book.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Air-conditioning</li>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Bath or shower</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
<li>Bathrobe &amp; slippers</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Safe</li>
</ul>
<p>Cots are available on request for approx. €15 per day, payable locally. If you're staying in Deluxe room, cots are free.</p>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>A tourist tax of approx. €4 per person (aged 15+) per night, for a maximum of 10 nights, is payable locally.</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Accessibility</strong></p>]]></roomsDescription>
